data.description: Splendid 3 / 2 split floorplan CBS home in the sought-after Becker/Gatlin area. and NO HOA! This home boasts tropical landscaping, a fully fenced yard, and a covered patio for all-weather entertaining! The kitchen touts SS appliances, an island, a pot rack, and a large pantry. The en suite bath features simulated wood floors a soaking tub, a separate shower, and double sinks. Enjoy the outdoors on your covered patio and a bar area ready for you and your guests to enjoy. A delightful home for entertaining and families to enjoy, share, and grow. Located in an idyllic neighborhood within a short distance of grocery stores, shopping, and all the conveniences this area has to offer. Bring your boat or RV, NO HOA!**The Dining Room Light and Curtain Rods do not convey. The Shed stays.
